default5.3.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultEnsure that exemptions reinforce the principles of the packaging and WFD and reinforce the principles of minimising resource use, recycling and recycled content. Again it is difficult to see how the present proposal meets these criteria.
